<html xmlns:MadCap="http://www.madcapsoftware.com/Schemas/MadCap.xsd">
    <body>
        <p>
            <MadCap:equation>$Days\ in\ year\ = days\ in\ year\ of\ the\ current\ day$</MadCap:equation>
        </p>
        <p>Either 365 or 366 for leap years i.e. if the current day falls in a leap year, the calculation will use 366 Days in Year. In non-leap years, the 365 days will be used.</p>
    </body>
</html>